text: FC Rodina Moscow () is a Russian football team based in Moscow. It was founded in 2019 as a senior squad of a pre-existing youth academy. For 2019–20 season, it received the license for the third-tier Russian Professional Football League. ==Current squad== As of 2 October 2020, according to the PFL website. ===Other players under contract=== ==References== ==External links== * Official site Category:Association football clubs established in 2019 Category:Football clubs in Russia Category:Football clubs in Moscow Category:2019 establishments in Russia
